1374
01:26:43,932 --> 01:26:46,298
No, it's not.

1375
01:26:46,367 --> 01:26:47,766
No.

1376
01:26:47,835 --> 01:26:50,633
Cos every time you smile,

1377
01:26:50,705 --> 01:26:53,265
or laugh,

1378
01:26:53,341 --> 01:26:55,775
